^ "Horse Racing". Korea Be Inspired. Korea Tourism Organization. 2013. Retrieved December 27, 2013. 
^ Jin, Dal Yong (2010). Korea's Online Gaming Empire. The MIT Press. p. 59. ISBN 9780262014762. 


