South Korea

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search

"Republic of Korea" and "ROK" redirect here. For the Democratic People's Republic of Korea, see North Korea. For other uses, see Korea and ROK (disambiguation).
Coordinates: 36°N 128°E﻿ / ﻿36°N 128°E﻿ / 36; 128



Republic of Korea
대한민국
大韓民國
Daehan Minguk







Flag



Emblem






Motto: "홍익인간 (弘益人間)" (Korean) (de facto)
"Benefit broadly in the human world/Devotion to the Welfare of Humanity"[1]




Anthem: Aegukga "애국가 (愛國歌)" (Korean) (de facto)
"Patriotic Song"














Government Emblem

대한민국정부 상징문양 (Korean)
Government Emblem of South Korea




